reviews.text: Definitely a nice place for dessert, the service is great and of course the dessert is above average.
Great local desserts with very reasonable price,  will go again!
Lots of choices local desserts and nice.
Very nice Hong Kong style dessert, and it's not that expensive compare to other similar products.
Nice HK style tong shui desserts in various choices at gd values.  I like the tofu desserts mixed with blk sesame soup most,  a must for me every visit.

reviews.text: 地方簡潔，甜品多款式，有水準，價錢大衆化，服務一般，門口可停車
地道糖水店，深水埗之選。
本地人很多，价格便宜，味道尚可，我吃杨枝甘露，分层上来的，要自己拌，柚子有点苦
由於老區，價錢方便尚算合理，亦算大眾化
Definitely a nice place for dessert, the service is great and of course the dessert is above average.
